room_title: Escape room "Tony’s Bistro" by MindGames Rock Hill in Rock Hill
room_address: 1807 Cherry Rd Suite #135 Rock Hill, SC 29723
room_description: Notorious Hit Man Rocco Calzone was supposed to get his payoff at Tony’s. When he got there he found an ambush waiting, and the Feds got the best of him. Somebody spilled the beans on Tony and they know the Half Million is still in the restaurant. They’ll be coming back for it soon. Don’t be there when they arrive.
